        <view class="text-content">折磨生出苦难，苦难又会加剧折磨，凡间这无穷的循环，将有我来终结！</view>
    </view>
    <view class="grid flex-sub padding-lr col-3 grid-square ">
        <view class="bg-img " style="background-image:url(https://ossweb-img.qq.com/images/lol/web201310/skin/big10006.jpg);" wx:for="{{9}}" wx:key="{{index}}"></view>
    </view>
    <view class="text-gray text-sm text-right padding">
        <text class="icon-attentionfill margin-lr-xs"></text>
        10
        <text class="icon-appreciatefill margin-lr-xs"></text>
        20
